1
00:00:07,580 --> 00:00:10,300
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,300 --> 00:00:14,260
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:15,020 --> 00:00:16,940
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:16,940 --> 00:00:19,940
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,340 --> 00:00:24,820
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:28,620
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:29,380 --> 00:00:30,940
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:30,940 --> 00:00:34,780
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:35,820 --> 00:00:39,460
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:43,780
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,260 --> 00:00:50,180
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:50,740 --> 00:00:54,340
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:54,580 --> 00:00:58,060
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:59,020 --> 00:01:05,020
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,220 --> 00:01:11,700
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:11,740 --> 00:01:16,700
=Episode 24=
(This story is entirely fictional.)

17
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,320
They've left.

18
00:01:34,780 --> 00:01:36,300
(Wedding)

19
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:38,000
Look sharp, everyone!

20
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:38,920
Tomorrow's the big day

21
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,560
for Mr. Li and Miss Zhou!

22
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:43,800
Move that one up a bit higher.

23
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:47,120
Give that corner a thorough cleaning.

24
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:47,920
Okay.

25
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:50,560
Come on, sweep it spotless,

26
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:56,680
(Wedding)

27
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:04,600
Mr. Li!

28
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,800
My lady sent me to ask

29
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:06,760
if you're all ready.

30
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,160
Right on time.

31
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:09,400
Chunxiang, take a look.

32
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,800
How do I look

33
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,680
in this?

34
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,080
You look so dashing today!

35
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:13,600
Chunxiang,

36
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,480
you're the head maidservant

37
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:16,280
of the Zhou Manor.

38
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,120
When you're out there,

39
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,400
you represent the Zhou Manor's image.

40
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:19,400
How can your choice of words

41
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,520
be so limited?

42
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,600
What should I say then?

43
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:23,480
You should say,

44
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:26,800
I'm dashing,

45
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,360
elegant,

46
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,960
and carry myself

47
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,400
with an air of distinction.

48
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:32,880
That's so much, Mr. Li.

49
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:33,920
I'll never remember all that.

50
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,080
Then just call me

51
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:40,000
the coolest man

52
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,400
in this world.

53
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,680
You're the coolest man, Mr. Li!

54
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,200
There, now that's more like it.

55
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,680
Here's

56
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,760
a little reward.

57
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,760
Thank you, Mr. Li!

58
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:51,480
You'll also be the richest man

59
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,680
in the world!

60
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,080
That's how you should talk,

61
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:54,480
got it?

62
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:55,640
Got it!

63
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:56,680
Mr. Li,

64
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:57,880
I'll also

65
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:59,280
dutifully stay by my lady's side

66
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,680
and serve as your chambermaid.

67
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:02,040
Whoa, that's absolutely
out of the question.

68
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:02,480
Chunxiang!

69
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,880
Chunxiang, what on earth are you saying?

70
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:06,920
Get over there!

71
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:08,680
Have you lost your mind?

72
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,200
So greedy and lecherous!

73
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,680
My dear.

74
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,000
Oh my.

75
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,000
As expected of the girl

76
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:43,400
I set my eyes on at first glance.

77
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:44,800
You're truly like a goddess
descended from the heavens.

78
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,240
My dear,

79
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:50,480
does the wedding dress fit comfortably?

80
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,280
Is there anywhere it feels off?

81
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,680
No. It's perfect.

82
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,480
That's good to know.

83
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:03,160
Yu, come over here.

84
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,000
Today

85
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:11,480
is our wedding.

86
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,240
What kind

87
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:14,960
of song should I sing later?

88
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:16,560
A song?

89
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,320
What songs

90
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:19,080
do you have?

91
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:20,560
Let me show you.

92
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:25,400
I've got "I've Got a Crush on You,"

93
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,680
"The Most Beautiful Anticipation,"

94
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,160
"Marry Me Today,"

95
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,280
and "This is Love".

96
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,800
Why have you written so many songs?

97
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:32,840
Next up,

98
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,640
I'm planning to hold concerts
all across Daqian

99
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,560
and rake in piles of cash.

100
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:38,040
Put the concerts aside for a moment.

101
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:39,880
Right now, the most important thing is

102
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:41,040
to hurry and produce

103
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,240
all that Gambiered Silk

104
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,440
that we pre-sold

105
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:44,920
and deliver it to our customers.

106
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:46,520
A few pre-orders?

107
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,160
How could something so trivial
possibly stump me?

108
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:50,480
Now that Prince Ning
and his rebel faction

109
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,640
have all been brought to justice,

110
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,480
Daqian can finally enjoy

111
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,840
peace and prosperity,

112
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:55,800
with songs and dances everywhere.

113
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,240
We have plenty of time.

114
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,240
Next,

115
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,560
I'm going to develop

116
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,520
even more novel gadgets

117
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:01,480
and take my good buddies along

118
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,720
to make money together.

119
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,640
Take your good buddies along?

120
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:11,080
Long Er, you may now

121
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,960
hold the post of Inspector,

122
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,440
but how can you just barge

123
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,240
into our Zhou Manor without knocking?

124
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,720
I never knock.

125
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:18,640
You...

126
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,440
An imperial edict has arrived.

127
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,520
A real imperial edict?

128
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,440
Obviously.

129
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:28,360
Forging an imperial decree
is a capital crime.

130
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,680
I've only been an official
for a few days.

131
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,840
You think I'd dare forge one?

132
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,720
Well, an edict arriving now...

133
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,200
It does make sense.

134
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,600
The emperor is my sworn brother.

135
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,360
It's my wedding.

136
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:39,040
I don't intend to ask him

137
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,280
to make me a prince

138
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:42,080
or some kind of royal kin.

139
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:42,760
At the very least,

140
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,000
he should be granting you

141
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,440
the title of Honored Lady, Yu,

142
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,680
and that's the bare minimum, right?

143
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,520
Go on, Long Er, read it.

144
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:52,040
Li Yunhe, for your meritorious service
protecting the throne,

145
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,200
I originally intended to confer upon you

146
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,880
the title of Prince Consort

147
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,440
to the Princess of Daqian.

148
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,840
However,
as you were betrothed beforehand,

149
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,120
it can only be set aside for now.

150
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:02,840
Now that I have reinstated
Gambiered Silk

151
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:03,720
as a royal tribute,

152
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,640
and the Princess's silk garments
have become soiled,

153
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:06,360
I hereby decree

154
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,360
that you deliver several sets

155
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:09,440
of the latest Gambiered Silk.

156
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:11,760
If they're not delivered

157
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,440
by sunset tomorrow,

158
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,320
you shall be executed immediately.

159
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:19,160
What kind of imperial edict is that?

160
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,960
Is that even a real edict?

161
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:21,400
Of course it's real.

162
00:06:21,840 --> 00:06:23,880
It's stamped
with the Imperial Jade Seal.

163
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:25,440
But...

164
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:26,800
But this doesn't

165
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,480
sound like something
Zhao Yunzhuo would say.

166
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,280
Buddy, watch your words.

167
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,560
This truly is an edict.

168
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:32,760
This seal

169
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,840
does seem genuine.

170
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:38,880
Long Er,

171
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,400
did you not tell Zhao Yunzhuo

172
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,640
that it's my wedding today?

173
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:42,360
Oh, right now is not the time

174
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,040
to be worrying about that.

175
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:46,560
Traveling from Feng City to the capital
is a long, grueling journey.

176
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:48,520
Finishing it within a single day
is absolutely impossible,

177
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,840
let alone delivering it in person.

178
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,640
That part actually isn't difficult.

179
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:55,040
Not difficult? You've got to be joking.

180
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:58,240
Don't you remember

181
00:06:58,440 --> 00:07:00,240
what I'm capable of?

182
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:08,160
How are you supposed to go?

183
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:12,360
Alright, I'm off.

184
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,160
Can this thing

185
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:16,640
reach the capital within a day?

186
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,640
Rest assured, it's guaranteed delivery.

187
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:19,320
Mr. Li,

188
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:20,720
you must come back soon.

189
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,520
My lady is still waiting
for your wedding night.

190
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:24,320
Whatever you do,
don't go to any brothels.

191
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:27,240
What kind of nonsense is that?

192
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,200
I definitely

193
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,240
can't make it back today.

194
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,440
But Chunxiang does have a point.

195
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:33,920
It's not proper to leave

196
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:36,520
my beautiful bride all alone
on our wedding night.

197
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,840
It's no big deal.

198
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,240
Are you sure?

199
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,360
Of course.

200
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:42,960
It's really high up there,

201
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,320
and you're not scared?

202
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,840
With you here, nothing scares me.

203
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:48,320
Let's go.

204
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:55,240
Head back on your own, Chunxiang.

205
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:56,120
Alright.

206
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,080
In the end,

207
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:29,680
he still became someone else's groom.

208
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:31,840
Zhou Xingyu,

209
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,240
don't think you get to have

210
00:08:34,680 --> 00:08:35,920
the man I couldn't have.

211
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:38,120
I bet that imperial edict I forged

212
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,520
will scare the life out of them.

213
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,040
Your Highness,

214
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:43,040
you can't just say things like that
so casually.

215
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:45,040
If the ministers find out,

216
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,400
they'll go right to His Majesty again

217
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,720
and report you
for neglecting your duties

218
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,840
and stirring up trouble.

219
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,000
Oh, get lost.

220
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:52,680
I'm the princess of Daqian.

221
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:54,920
My brother is the emperor of Daqian.

222
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:57,480
What's wrong with me
using his jade seal just once?

223
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:05,240
Come here. What is that?

224
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:17,240
Li Yunhe? Yu?

225
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:19,280
How are they up in the sky?

226
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,040
Imperial restricted grounds!

227
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:31,640
Trespassers shall be executed
without mercy!

228
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,880
Stop!

229
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:37,360
Get out of my way!

230
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,920
Li Yunhe, Yu,

231
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:43,240
what are you doing here?

232
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,320
Your Highness.

233
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:47,240
By His Majesty's imperial decree,
we have come

234
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:49,160
(Tang Xian Gambiered Silk)
specially to deliver the Gambiered Silk.

235
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,320
Gambiered Silk?

236
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,280
You actually brought it?

237
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,440
Of course.

238
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:55,120
Who do you think I am?

239
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,360
Is that another one

240
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,360
of those bizarre contraptions

241
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,560
you've been tinkering with?

242
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,280
That's a hot air balloon. It can travel

243
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,880
a thousand miles in a single day.

244
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:02,720
That's right.

245
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:03,240
It's precisely because

246
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,680
of that hot air balloon

247
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:05,960
that we could reach the capital

248
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,240
before sunset.

249
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:09,640
Well, that's pretty neat.

250
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:11,040
This thing

251
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:13,760
can go from Feng City to the capital
within a single day?

252
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:16,160
Li Yunhe, doesn't that mean

253
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:17,440
I can pop over to Feng City
and hang out with you

254
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,360
whenever I want?

255
00:10:19,040 --> 00:10:19,600
I never said that.

256
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,280
I told you Li Yunhe would find a way.

257
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,240
- Greetings, Your Majesty.
- Greetings, Your Majesty.

258
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:28,160
I offer you the grandest of salutes.

259
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,160
You may dispense with the formalities.

260
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:35,320
Thank you, Your Majesty.

261
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:43,360
Your Majesty,
what's the meaning of this?

262
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,120
I learned it from you,

263
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,360
earning a little extra on the side,

264
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:48,000
just for a bit of fun.

265
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:52,520
(Being the emperor sure is nice.)

266
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:53,920
(With a single command,)

267
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:55,240
(he's got me traveling a thousand miles)

268
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,040
(from Feng City to the capital)

269
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:57,560
(on my own wedding day.)

270
00:10:58,040 --> 00:10:58,720
Li Yunhe.

271
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:01,440
Today was supposed to be
your wedding day.

272
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:04,240
Yet, because
of the Princess's idle prank,

273
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:06,680
you and your wife had to
undertake this long, exhausting journey.

274
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:10,320
I'm deeply ashamed.

275
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:12,160
So it was you?

276
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,280
Yu,

277
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:17,040
I didn't mean any harm.

278
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,640
You're not

279
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,840
upset with me, are you?

280
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,720
No, not at all.

281
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:24,920
(As if I wouldn't be.)

282
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:27,040
Since you're here anyway...

283
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:29,520
Attendants, take them to change.

284
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,520
Yes, Your Majesty.

285
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:39,720
Whoa...

286
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:43,920
Yunzhuo,

287
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:45,480
all this was prepared for me?

288
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,720
Are you satisfied

289
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,920
with my arrangements?

290
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,840
Worthy of my sworn brother.

291
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:51,600
We must

292
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:53,160
have a proper drink together today.

293
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:54,120
No rush.

294
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:56,840
Look who's here.

295
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,640
- Greetings, Your Majesty.
- Greetings, Your Majesty.

296
00:11:58,640 --> 00:11:59,320
Mother?

297
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:01,840
Huaijin? How come you're here?

298
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:03,000
Gambiered Silk's reputation

299
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,280
has already taken off in Feng City.

300
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:06,560
And now that it's been reinstated
as a royal tribute,

301
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:07,560
His Majesty wanted to promote it

302
00:12:07,560 --> 00:12:09,040
here in the capital as well,

303
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:09,760
so he invited

304
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:10,760
us here.

305
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:11,760
That's fantastic!

306
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:15,440
Did you invite them here,

307
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,200
or did you summon them

308
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,680
with an imperial decree?

309
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:18,880
What do you think?

310
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:20,240
Easy now!

311
00:12:20,680 --> 00:12:22,040
I've got serious business
to attend to tonight.

312
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:24,320
Alright now.

313
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,480
Everyone's here now.

314
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:27,480
Let the wedding begin!

315
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,320
Yes! Let the wedding begin!

316
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,160
Not so fast!

317
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:33,440
Li Yunhe,

318
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:35,640
even though the Gambiered Silk
you sent today

319
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:37,160
is genuinely quite comfortable,

320
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,000
I still

321
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,880
cannot accept this.

322
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,240
Your Highness,

323
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,920
what exactly is there to not accept?

324
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:48,040
When it comes to matters of the heart,

325
00:12:48,560 --> 00:12:49,720
there's simply no logic to them.

326
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:51,720
I don't care.

327
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:52,880
Here's the deal.

328
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:55,560
Everyone puts on
the Gambiered Silk you brought,

329
00:12:55,560 --> 00:12:57,160
then wears a veil.

330
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:59,120
You have just a quarter's time

331
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:00,240
to pick out Yu.

332
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:01,160
Are you game or not?

333
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:03,240
Good idea, Your Highness.

334
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:06,840
Xingyu, you know full well

335
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:08,840
I've admired Mr. Li
for a very long time.

336
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:12,040
You don't mind if I like him, do you?

337
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:13,560
Song Huaijin, has your brain

338
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:14,880
gone haywire again?

339
00:13:14,880 --> 00:13:15,960
It drifts past vermilion chambers,

340
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,120
dips low through carved lattice windows,

341
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,520
shining upon the sleepless.

342
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:19,880
Ever since I saw Mr. Li

343
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:21,280
at Chunfeng Pavilion,

344
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:22,640
I have found no sleep at night,

345
00:13:22,920 --> 00:13:23,960
only wishing to...

346
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:24,960
Stop reciting.

347
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,840
He's not going to be with you.

348
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:29,560
Li Yunhe.

349
00:13:30,880 --> 00:13:31,680
Well?

350
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,520
What do you mean, "well"?

351
00:13:33,680 --> 00:13:34,960
I'm not taking multiple wives.

352
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,160
No way I'm taking any of them.

353
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:36,960
I refuse!

354
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:39,480
This brooks no refusal.

355
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:40,720
Ladies!

356
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,360
On my command, seize him!

357
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,960
What are you doing?

358
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:46,920
In fact, Mr. Li,

359
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:49,080
I've admired you

360
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,240
for a very long time too.

361
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:55,760
Hey, why are you involved here?

362
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:58,440
Do you have a problem?

363
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,040
Yunzhuo.

364
00:14:01,680 --> 00:14:01,920
This...

365
00:14:01,920 --> 00:14:03,320
This wedding

366
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,920
might have to be postponed a few days.

367
00:14:06,280 --> 00:14:07,000
- Li Yunhe!
- Li Yunhe!

368
00:14:07,040 --> 00:14:07,840
- Mr. Li!
- Mr. Li!

369
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,480
- Mr. Li!
- Stop running!

370
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:12,640
Your Majesty, if there's nothing else,

371
00:14:12,640 --> 00:14:13,880
I'll be heading back now.

372
00:14:15,640 --> 00:14:16,480
My dear son-in-law!

373
00:14:54,900 --> 00:14:58,500
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

374
00:14:58,660 --> 00:15:01,860
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

375
00:15:02,380 --> 00:15:05,100
♪Who took the March rain♪

376
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:08,700
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

377
00:15:09,060 --> 00:15:11,860
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

378
00:15:12,020 --> 00:15:15,220
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

379
00:15:16,100 --> 00:15:22,020
♪Needle and thread
stitch away the marks of time♪

380
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:25,500
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

381
00:15:25,740 --> 00:15:28,580
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

382
00:15:28,740 --> 00:15:31,020
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

383
00:15:31,020 --> 00:15:35,220
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

384
00:15:35,300 --> 00:15:38,580
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

385
00:15:38,740 --> 00:15:41,860
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

386
00:15:42,380 --> 00:15:45,300
♪In this life I'd be a cloud-tailor♪

387
00:15:45,460 --> 00:15:51,980
♪Never failing the stars,
nor failing you♪

388
00:16:18,260 --> 00:16:21,780
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

389
00:16:22,020 --> 00:16:25,180
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

390
00:16:25,780 --> 00:16:28,500
♪Who took the March rain♪

391
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:32,020
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

392
00:16:32,420 --> 00:16:35,300
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

393
00:16:35,380 --> 00:16:39,100
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

394
00:16:39,140 --> 00:16:42,420
♪Warp and weft entwine,
one shuttle, one dream♪

395
00:16:42,420 --> 00:16:45,380
♪As seasons change♪

396
00:16:45,380 --> 00:16:49,020
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

397
00:16:49,020 --> 00:16:51,860
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

398
00:16:51,940 --> 00:16:54,500
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

399
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:58,580
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

400
00:16:58,580 --> 00:17:01,900
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

401
00:17:01,900 --> 00:17:05,620
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

402
00:17:06,020 --> 00:17:09,140
♪Washing away
a lifetime of wear and tear♪

403
00:17:09,140 --> 00:17:12,020
♪Only for you♪

404
00:17:12,020 --> 00:17:15,620
♪On the street of golden honors,
the music rises♪

405
00:17:15,740 --> 00:17:18,500
♪The moon moves west
beyond the pavilion♪

406
00:17:18,620 --> 00:17:21,180
♪Wine runs dry, yet the revelry lingers♪

407
00:17:21,180 --> 00:17:25,260
♪In silk, I seek a kindred soul♪

408
00:17:25,260 --> 00:17:28,580
♪The rain has ceased,
clouds begin to clear♪

409
00:17:28,620 --> 00:17:31,980
♪The fragrant silk billows
under the low-hung stars♪

410
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:38,500
♪I'd cut the clouds and morning glow
to drape over you♪

411
00:17:39,580 --> 00:17:43,700
♪A single bolt of silk becomes♪

412
00:17:44,980 --> 00:17:49,500
♪Your wedding gown♪
